gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 126, Lakers 115
gameRecap.excerpt: Despite Anthony Daviss 40 points, 13 rebounds and four assists, the Lakers fall to the Celtics, 126-115.  Kristaps Porzingis (28 points, 11 rebounds) and Jayson Tatum (25 points, eight rebounds, seven assists) combine for 53 points for the Celtics in the victory.  LeBron James added 16 points, nine rebounds and eight assists for the Lakers.  The Celtics improve to 23-6 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 16-15
